  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients of both sexes and age 20 years and above with paraumblical hernia Defect size
             3 to 6cm in greatest diameter

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  defect size less than 3cm or greater than 6 cm in greatest diameter Obstructed or
             strangulated hernia Uncontrolled diabetes
